column5: Well another exciting dump trip in the books.Of course always check the dock to.Not much has changed.Still lots of ice.Small lake up Blue Lake road that's still tight to and most locals keep a eye on that lake.Once it's ice free Eagle follows about a week later.So if the small lake maybe goes in a week then Eagle would open a week later.So just roughly it could take till end of second week of May.Time will tell
It'll be all good by June 16th! Later, Jay
It will be awesome then Jay.
It ALWAYS is! I have never had a bad trip to Canada. We have had a few things unexpected happen, but, I wouldn't let it bother me in the least. Later, Jay
16" on Red Lake as of yesterday. Local thinks May 12 ice off.
